data.description: Welcome to an extraordinary and elegant residence that exudes sophistication and charm. This small mansion is not just a home; it's an experience waiting to be savored. As you step inside, you are immediately enveloped in an ambiance of luxury and refinement. The heart of this magnificent abode is a grand dining room, where fine dining with family and friends becomes an art form. With a commanding view of the entrance, this space sets the stage for memorable gatherings and culinary delights. Picture yourself sharing laughter and stories around a beautifully set table, bathed in the soft glow of exquisite chandeliers. Moving on to the living room, you'll find an inviting oasis centered around a graceful fireplace. This room is a testament to timeless elegance, with its tasteful decor and plush furnishings. It's the perfect place to unwind with a glass of wine, enveloped in the warm embrace of the crackling fire. Adjacent to the living room, a cozy breakfast area beckons you. It offers a panoramic view of the deck and the lush backyard, where you can start your day with nature's beauty as your backdrop. The second fireplace here adds a touch of warmth and comfort to your morning routine. Retreat to the master bedroom and bath suite, a sanctuary that boasts vaulted ceilings and opulent amenities. Imagine soaking away the day's stresses in a whirlpool tub or indulging in a rejuvenating separate shower. This space is a testament to relaxation and tranquility, designed to pamper you in every way possible. Should you need a private workspace or an extra bedroom, there's a versatile 5th bedroom or office on the main level. It's a place where productivity meets elegance, making remote work a true pleasure.Descending to the lower level, you'll discover a world of entertainment and leisure. A media room awaits your cinematic adventures, offering the ultimate in-home movie experience. The lower level also has a half bath with tasteful tile floors and a spacious recreation room.
